{"tid":1412251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[提升士氣] 今朝老細打黎我問佢返唔返工，俾佢訓話訓左2分鐘","createTime":"2019-08-05T05:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T08:20:26.000Z","uid":291104,"like":153,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"654bd50a497fba058fd855d61c019f47fa495219","tid":1412251,"uid":291104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"Sorry有少少標題黨，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但好想打出黎俾Ｄ正能量大家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，<br />\n在下做野間公司星期五都出左EMAIL，算係對８５有不反對通知書，<br />\n我地TEAM都識做清哂手頭上Ｄ急野，但因為今個星期老細咁岩放大假，唔可以完全成ｔｅａｍ真空，唯有拎埋電腦返屋企，準備Home office。<br />\n今朝準時打開電腦，見到都冇咩人返，一直都好地地。<br />\n點知過左一陣，同team個細路話有front office 追佢拎野，因為係文件正本，<br />\n又話一定要今日要，即係一定要有人親自返去拎俾佢啦。<br />\n我地即刻屌哂鬼，但都冇乎，唔通真係唔理佢，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依個時候我唯有message我正在海外放假的老細，<br />\n同佢講如果我返我要打的架，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢居然話：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我同你講！你地個個都　唔　准　返　！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地又唔係今日都先今日要，上個星期公司出哂email都知今日會咁，自己都唔準備怪得邊個！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之你地嘅人身安全係我最重視嘅野！公司都話左係！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地一個都 唔 准 返 ！！This is my order！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你出到去有咩冬瓜豆腐，我點同你父母交待，我攞咩賠返俾你父母？？！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你同佢地講，聽朝先俾佢！我講嘅！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（然後ｒｅｐｅａｔ，下刪１００００字訓話）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我果下．．．．．．<br />\n雙眼發光，秒變心心眼．．．<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（利申，絲打）<br />\n<br />\n再黎多個彩蛋：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴晚屋企開飯，<br />\n我突然先醒起問阿媽：<br />\n我：弊！連登話聽日話唔好幫襯開鋪果ｄ，但你今日有冇買埋聽日嘅送？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">媽：梗係有啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：咁叻？！<br />\n媽：我仲叫埋ｄ師奶今日買埋，聽日唔好幫襯開鋪果ｄ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：好勁．．．．<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n媽：仲叫左佢地聽日唔好去飲茶！唔好俾佢地賺！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我突然覺得，我上世人應該做左好多好事．．．．好感恩．．．<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家加油！香港唔可以再輸！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896802b621e88f5e66f6cbdded1b91026ca1eb06","tid":1412251,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:59:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ac009ae42692828e5453cbc205ffe40ba51fc05","tid":1412251,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdaccb8b6b14ceb9fe0342fbcf9340643fe2c70f","tid":1412251,"uid":86282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:03:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2918b4b05d9b978f0a97546e52fee415805cf72e","tid":1412251,"uid":7567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:07:51.000Z","msg":"羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c477ef2d0ad14be0d6ed1ebbfd3babe11b0750","tid":1412251,"uid":291104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:15:50.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1d5a8cb0403c646093a4e44214e6a6187a39dd57","tid":1412251,"uid":58558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:20:16.000Z","msg":"絲打老母好波"},{"pid":"23777de2ad898ca0034c0762eb85c5e06b3cbb87","tid":1412251,"uid":291104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1d5a8cb0403c646093a4e44214e6a6187a39dd57","tid":1412251,"uid":58558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:20:16.000Z","msg":"絲打老母好波"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:22:35.000Z","msg":"我兩老真係好正，<br />\n一早起身我喺房做緊野，<br />\n已經聽到佢地兩個喺廳一路睇直播一路屌林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe8a415b66a498cff3a96af7b07240b75328f6b","tid":1412251,"uid":252031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif